  <div class="home-page-card"><h3 class="text-center">Who we are</h3><p class="text-center align-center">Ringr instantly links teams with players. Through our advanced algorithm we make the right connection, leaving you to get the job done on the pitch.</p><%= image_tag "cricket_amateur.png", :id => 'cricket-image' %></div>
